Package agh.alleviation.model

Class Order

java.lang.Object
agh.alleviation.model.EntityObject
agh.alleviation.model.Order
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Externalizable, java.io.Serializable
@Entity
public class Order
extends EntityObject
Class responsible for representation of customer's orders. In one order there may be many tickets, but one order can be bought only by one user.
Author:
Ksenia Fiodarava
See Also:
Ticket, Customer, Serialized Form
